    public static class Invokes

namespace Pulumi.Azure
{
    public static class Config
    {
        public static System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<string> AuxiliaryTenantIds { get; set; }
        public static string? ClientCertificatePassword { get; set; }
        public static string? ClientCertificatePath { get; set; }
        public static string? ClientId { get; set; }
        public static string? ClientSecret { get; set; }
        public static bool? DisableCorrelationRequestId { get; set; }
        public static bool? DisableTerraformPartnerId { get; set; }
        public static string? Environment { get; set; }
        public static Pulumi.Azure.Config.Types.Features? Features { get; set; }
        public static string? Location { get; set; }
        public static string? MsiEndpoint { get; set; }
        public static string? PartnerId { get; set; }
        public static bool? SkipCredentialsValidation { get; set; }
        public static bool? SkipProviderRegistration { get; set; }
        public static bool? StorageUseAzuread { get; set; }
        public static string? SubscriptionId { get; set; }
        public static string? TenantId { get; set; }
        public static bool? UseMsi { get; set; }
        public static class Types
        {
            public class Features
            {
                public Features() { }
                public Pulumi.Azure.Config.Types.FeaturesKeyVault? KeyVault { get; set; }
                public Pulumi.Azure.Config.Types.FeaturesVirtualMachine? VirtualMachine { get; set; }
                public Pulumi.Azure.Config.Types.FeaturesVirtualMachineScaleSet? VirtualMachineScaleSet { get; set; }
            }
            public class FeaturesKeyVault
            {
                public FeaturesKeyVault() { }
                public bool? PurgeSoftDeleteOnDestroy { get; set; }
                public bool? RecoverSoftDeletedKeyVaults { get; set; }
            }
            public class FeaturesVirtualMachine
            {
                public FeaturesVirtualMachine() { }
                public bool DeleteOsDiskOnDeletion { get; set; }
            }
            public class FeaturesVirtualMachineScaleSet
            {
                public FeaturesVirtualMachineScaleSet() { }
                public bool RollInstancesWhenRequired { get; set; }
            }
        }
    }
    public class Provider : Pulumi.ProviderResource
    {
        public Provider(string name, Pulumi.Azure.ProviderArgs? args = null, Pulumi.CustomResourceOptions? options = null) { }
    }
    public sealed class ProviderArgs : Pulumi.ResourceArgs
    {
        public ProviderArgs() { }
        public Pulumi.InputList<string> AuxiliaryTenantIds { get; set; }
        [Pulumi.Input("clientCertificatePassword", false, false)]
        public Pulumi.Input<string>? ClientCertificatePassword { get; set; }

        public readonly System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<string> AcceptedProtocols;
        public readonly bool? Enabled;
        public readonly Pulumi.Azure.FrontDoor.Outputs.FrontdoorRoutingRuleForwardingConfiguration? ForwardingConfiguration;
        public readonly System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<string> FrontendEndpoints;
        public readonly string? Id;
        public readonly string Name;
        public readonly System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<string> PatternsToMatches;
        public readonly Pulumi.Azure.FrontDoor.Outputs.FrontdoorRoutingRuleRedirectConfiguration? RedirectConfiguration;
    }
    [Pulumi.OutputType]
    public sealed class FrontdoorRoutingRuleForwardingConfiguration
    {
        public readonly string BackendPoolName;
        public readonly bool? CacheEnabled;
        public readonly string? CacheQueryParameterStripDirective;
        public readonly bool? CacheUseDynamicCompression;
        public readonly string? CustomForwardingPath;
        public readonly string? ForwardingProtocol;
    }
    [Pulumi.OutputType]
    public sealed class FrontdoorRoutingRuleRedirectConfiguration
    {
        public readonly string? CustomFragment;
        public readonly string? CustomHost;
        public readonly string? CustomPath;
        public readonly string? CustomQueryString;
        public readonly string RedirectProtocol;
        public readonly string RedirectType;
    }
}

        public readonly string? AutoGrow;
        public readonly int? BackupRetentionDays;
        public readonly string? GeoRedundantBackup;
        public readonly int StorageMb;
    }
